<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 08:10:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队将记者带到“哈马斯羞辱我们人质”的广场。这是错误的广场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-took-control-of-square-where-hamas-humiliated-hostages-but-it-was-the-wrong-one/0000018c-5597-db23-ad9f-7ddf39090000</link><description>哈马斯高调释放人质的巴勒斯坦广场位于巴勒斯坦广场以南一英里多处，以色列军队将其夷为平地，并在巴勒斯坦广场举行了象征性的光明节仪式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 07:38:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-took-control-of-square-where-hamas-humiliated-hostages-but-it-was-the-wrong-one/0000018c-5597-db23-ad9f-7ddf39090000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯日渐衰弱，以色列军方想知道如何向公众推销加沙的胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-wearing-thin-as-israels-military-wonders-how-to-sell-victory-to-the-public/0000018c-5593-df2f-adac-ffbff1760000</link><description>以色列正在与美国的时间赛跑，它试图在美国对战争的支持耗尽之前完成其军事目标。也希望国际社会能够清醒过来，共同努力解决北部边境问题</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 06:34:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-wearing-thin-as-israels-military-wonders-how-to-sell-victory-to-the-public/0000018c-5593-df2f-adac-ffbff1760000</guid></item><item><title>西方外交官发出警告，内塔尼亚胡发言人否认以色列部长驱逐加沙的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-spokesman-denies-existence-of-plans-to-expel-palestinians-from-gaza/0000018c-552c-db23-ad9f-7dfc51eb0000</link><description>在以色列多位部长暗中明确提及从加沙转移巴勒斯坦人之后，这种否认受到以色列西方盟友的欢迎。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-spokesman-denies-existence-of-plans-to-expel-palestinians-from-gaza/0000018c-552c-db23-ad9f-7dfc51eb0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列国防军预备役士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；黎巴嫩火箭袭击以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article-live/syria-israel-attacked-in-the-damascus-area-idf-intercepted-aircraft-from-lebanon/0000018c-56c4-df4b-a78e-d7c70bf50000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，已确定从黎巴嫩发射了 8 枚火箭，其中两枚被拦截，其余击中开阔地区 ■ 以色列军队在加沙杀死了哈马斯高级指挥官 ■ 叙利亚报道以色列在大马士革附近发动袭击，叙利亚防空系统拦截了以色列火箭 ■ 又有四名以色列国防军士兵丧生，其中三名在加沙战斗和一场军用车祸 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称 17,700 人死亡，48,700 人受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 03:54:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-11/ty-article-live/syria-israel-attacked-in-the-damascus-area-idf-intercepted-aircraft-from-lebanon/0000018c-56c4-df4b-a78e-d7c70bf50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列农民眼睁睁地看着他们一生的劳动被毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-farmers-are-watching-their-lifes-work-being-destroyed/0000018c-547e-db23-ad9f-7cfebc8c0000</link><description>来自加沙地带以外社区的一些以色列农民也受到以色列-哈马斯战争的严重打击，但他们的损失不会得到全额赔偿。他们说，他们重建并再次种植当地农产品的机会很小</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 20:20:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-farmers-are-watching-their-lifes-work-being-destroyed/0000018c-547e-db23-ad9f-7cfebc8c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军报告自 10 月 7 日以来有 1,593 人受伤，但医院数据要高得多</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-reports-1-593-wounded-since-october-7-but-hospital-data-is-much-higher/0000018c-552d-df4b-a78e-d52f47ac0000</link><description>与过去的冲突和战争不同，以色列军队隐瞒了受伤士兵及其状况的报告。在《国土报》报道称军方拒绝这样做后，军方才公布了这一信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 20:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-reports-1-593-wounded-since-october-7-but-hospital-data-is-much-higher/0000018c-552d-df4b-a78e-d52f47ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵周五在加沙战斗中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-inflicted-friday-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-5534-df2f-adac-ff3d51350000</link><description>纳坦内尔·梅纳赫姆·埃坦 (Nethenel Menachem Eitan) 中尉是军官训练学校格芬营的一名学员，也是 Zichron Menachem 癌症儿童非营利组织的杰出志愿者</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 19:39:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-inflicted-friday-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-5534-df2f-adac-ff3d51350000</guid></item><item><title>计算以色列-哈马斯战争中人命的价值</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-10/ty-article/.highlight/calculating-what-a-human-life-is-worth-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-544f-db23-ad9f-7cdf4a910000</link><description>尽管它们不足以捕捉整个生命，但 10 月 7 日和加沙战争的数字是不可避免的——而这些冰冷的数字现在更多地用来描述死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 18:35:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-10/ty-article/.highlight/calculating-what-a-human-life-is-worth-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-544f-db23-ad9f-7cdf4a910000</guid></item><item><title>与警方的说法相矛盾，在被以色列士兵杀害的男子尸体中发现子弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/contradicting-police-claim-bullet-found-in-body-of-man-killed-by-israeli-soldier/0000018c-5460-df2f-adac-fe6d2d720000</link><description>以色列士兵阿维亚德·弗里贾 (Aviad Frija) 在一次枪击袭击中多次向尤瓦尔·凯斯特尔曼开枪，声称他认为自己是恐怖分子。警方表示不需要尸检后，他的尸体被埋葬，宪兵队得出相反结论后，他的尸体被挖掘出来</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 17:27:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/contradicting-police-claim-bullet-found-in-body-of-man-killed-by-israeli-soldier/0000018c-5460-df2f-adac-fe6d2d720000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡抨击普京俄罗斯的“反以色列”立场和伊朗关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-putin-for-russias-anti-israel-stance-iran-ties/0000018c-53e5-d6bd-a1ad-7bf7f45e0000</link><description>克里姆林宫去年 10 月接待了哈马斯官员代表团，此后一直保持与伊朗的联系，克里姆林宫表示，这次 50 分钟的通话主要围绕加沙的人道主义危机</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 15:34:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-putin-for-russias-anti-israel-stance-iran-ties/0000018c-53e5-d6bd-a1ad-7bf7f45e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军透露，自 10 月 7 日以来，已有 1,593 名以色列士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/1-593-israeli-soldiers-wounded-since-october-7-idf-reveals/0000018c-5416-df2f-adac-fe3fbe6d0000</link><description>与过去的冲突和战争不同，以色列军队隐瞒了受伤士兵及其状况的报告。在《国土报》报道称军方拒绝这样做后，军方才公布了这一信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 15:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/1-593-israeli-soldiers-wounded-since-october-7-idf-reveals/0000018c-5416-df2f-adac-fe3fbe6d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙最古老的清真寺之一在战斗中受损；以色列国防军称，它被哈马斯使用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/one-of-gazas-oldest-mosques-damaged-in-fighting-it-was-used-by-hamas-idf-says/0000018c-53d7-db23-ad9f-7bdf62f30000</link><description>视频显示，这座清真寺被认为是加沙地带最重要的历史建筑之一，但其地基已被摧毁，内部大厅已被完全摧毁。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 14:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/one-of-gazas-oldest-mosques-damaged-in-fighting-it-was-used-by-hamas-idf-says/0000018c-53d7-db23-ad9f-7bdf62f30000</guid></item><item><title>十字军在圣地吃什么？考古学家亲自动手寻找答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-10/ty-article-magazine/what-did-crusaders-eat-in-the-holy-land-archaeologists-get-hands-dirty-to-find-out/0000018c-536f-df2f-adac-ff6f59280000</link><description>以色列的新研究揭示了十字军在繁荣时期的消费情况，以及在马穆鲁克人将十字军困在阿波罗尼亚城堡中的围困期间的消费情况</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 12:23:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-10/ty-article-magazine/what-did-crusaders-eat-in-the-holy-land-archaeologists-get-hands-dirty-to-find-out/0000018c-536f-df2f-adac-ff6f59280000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡必须在政治上被摧毁，否则以色列将与他一起灭亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-must-be-politically-destroyed-or-israel-will-go-down-with-him/0000018c-530f-db23-ad9f-7bdfeca10000</link><description>关于总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的最大神话之一是他是一位精明的政治家。他对伊朗、美国、哈马斯和其他关键领域的外交政策表明恰恰相反</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 11:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-must-be-politically-destroyed-or-israel-will-go-down-with-him/0000018c-530f-db23-ad9f-7bdfeca10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称摩萨德帮助挫败了伊朗在塞浦路斯的恐怖阴谋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/two-iranians-questioned-over-suspected-plots-to-attack-israelis-in-cyprus/0000018c-5349-db23-ad9f-7bd9a8230000</link><description>据当地媒体报道，据信这两人正处于收集有关以色列潜在目标情报的早期阶段。塞浦路斯是成千上万以色列人的热门度假和投资目的地</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 11:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/two-iranians-questioned-over-suspected-plots-to-attack-israelis-in-cyprus/0000018c-5349-db23-ad9f-7bd9a8230000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装对以色列船只的威胁可能导致红海全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/houthi-threats-against-israel-bound-ships-could-lead-to-war-in-the-red-sea/0000018c-5124-df2f-adac-ff2d1f120000</link><description>胡塞武装警告说，任何前往以色列的船只都是目标，这可能会使红海成为新的军事对抗的焦点。可能需要的是在不久的将来展示武力，这也将对抗伊朗持续的威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 07:29:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/houthi-threats-against-israel-bound-ships-could-lead-to-war-in-the-red-sea/0000018c-5124-df2f-adac-ff2d1f120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙击毙哈马斯指挥官；叙利亚：以色列袭击大马士革附近</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article-live/israels-ground-offensive-in-gaza-deepens-as-arab-eu-leaders-push-for-a-cease-fire/0000018c-5187-df2f-adac-ffaf03700000</link><description>随着越来越多的国家呼吁立即停火，以色列国防军在加沙的地面行动仍在进行中 ■ 美国在否决联合国安理会停火决议一天后跳过国会审查批准向以色列出售坦克炮弹 ■ 也门胡塞武装表示一切红海中前往以色列的船只被视为目标 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称 17,700 人死亡，48,700 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 06:35:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article-live/israels-ground-offensive-in-gaza-deepens-as-arab-eu-leaders-push-for-a-cease-fire/0000018c-5187-df2f-adac-ffaf03700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列打击加沙哈马斯的时间已所剩无几，美国的耐心已所剩无几</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/streching-u-s-patience-time-is-running-out-on-israels-campaign-against-hamas-in-gaza/0000018c-506d-df4b-a78e-d16f72cf0000</link><description>美国否决了联合国安理会的停火要求，并提出向以色列提供 45,000 枚坦克炮弹的协议，但白宫对以色列的支持并非无限</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 04:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/streching-u-s-patience-time-is-running-out-on-israels-campaign-against-hamas-in-gaza/0000018c-506d-df4b-a78e-d16f72cf0000</guid></item><item><title>两名阿拉伯裔以色列兄弟在以色列北部城市海法涉嫌双重凶杀案中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/two-arab-israeli-brothers-shot-dead-in-suspected-double-homicide-in-haifa/0000018c-505f-df4b-a78e-d15fc18e0000</link><description>萨米尔·赛义德 (Samir Said) 和萨梅赫·赛义德 (Sameh Said) 两兄弟在城市停车场被红大卫盾会医护人员发现，情况危急，随后被宣布当场死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 21:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/two-arab-israeli-brothers-shot-dead-in-suspected-double-homicide-in-haifa/0000018c-505f-df4b-a78e-d15fc18e0000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生； 10 月 7 日，一名士兵因受伤死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-soldier-dies-of-wounds-inflicted-on-oct-7/0000018c-4fa4-df4b-a78e-dfa7483c0000</link><description>阵亡士兵中包括以色列战时内阁成员加迪·艾森科特的侄子，他在加沙地带南部的战斗中阵亡两天前失去了自己的儿子</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 20:13:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-soldier-dies-of-wounds-inflicted-on-oct-7/0000018c-4fa4-df4b-a78e-dfa7483c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>